INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(9,'Corporate Profile','Corporate Profile','IT Bangla Ltd. is a premier IT Education and Software Solution House, Dhaka, Bangladesh, which has more than 10 years of experience in IT field of Bangladesh. Just ten years ago, IT Bangla started its journey by introducing its services: IT training, Software development and Total IT solution. Since then, IT Bangla has experienced extraordinary growth; averaging twelve per cent annual enrolment increases.  A highly skilled management team and well-qualified Board of Directors manage the affairs of the company. All projects in turnkey basis are managed and controlled by a strong project management team comprising of a Project Director, Technical Director, Project Manager and Co-coordinator. In addition to the members of the Board, the management is being supported by a combination of well groomed and skilled IT, administration, finance, research and marketing staff members.','1','corporate_profile','corporate_profile','1',2,'IT Bangla Ltd. is a premier IT Education and Software Solution House, Dhaka, Bangladesh, which has more than 10 years of experience in IT field of Bangladesh. Just ten years ago, IT Bangla started its journey by introducing its services: IT training, Software development and Total IT solution. Since then, IT Bangla has experienced extraordinary growth; averaging twelve per cent annual enrolment increases. INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(10,'Background','Background','T Bangla Ltd. is a premier IT Education and Software Solution House, Dhaka, Bangladesh, which has more than 8 years of experience in IT field of Bangladesh. It is established in the year 2000. From that time, it provides quality services in the field of IT. ITB started its journey back in 2000 with the vision of creating a proper IT work force in order to sustain its future activities in IT industry in Bangladesh. ITB has successfully trained and developed 2500s of skilled IT professionals who are currently engaged in the ICT industry in home and abroad. As one of the major player in the IT Education services in the country, ITB has the unique advantage of organizing a large pool of trained and experienced IT professionals for a given project. ITB is affiliated with a renowned international university Assumption University of Thailand to provide international standard quality education services in Bangladesh.','1','corporate_profile','1','1',2,'T Bangla Ltd. is a premier IT Education and Software Solution House, Dhaka, Bangladesh, which has more than 8 years of experience in IT field of Bangladesh. It is established in the year 2000. From that time, it provides quality services in the field of IT. ITB started its journey back in 2000 with the vision of creating a proper IT work force in order to sustain its future activities in IT industry in Bangladesh. INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(11,'Mission','Mission','The mission of IT Bangla is to provide high quality of training on different courses to build the career of anyone in IT field, make well design software and high quality networking and hardware trouble shooting solution.  IT Bangla is such a Limited. It serves its clients and trainees as a trusted ally, providing them with the loyalty of a business partner and the economic. We make sure that our clients and trainees have what they need to run their businesses and to build their career as well as possible, with maximum efficiency and reliability.  Many of our information applications are mission critical, so we give assurance that we will be there when they need us.','1','career2','1','1',2,'The mission of IT Bangla is to provide high quality of training on different courses to build the career of anyone in IT field, make well design software and high quality networking and hardware trouble shooting solution. INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(12,'Aims','Aims','To be the number one IT company in Bangladesh within four years.  Provide services in accordance with the agreed quality and 90% projects completed within agreed time frame per annum.  Achievement of Key Performance Indicator (KPI) targets for each department.  Provide high quality of training and make this centre one of the top training centre on Bangladesh.  Establish a logical, flexible, and responsive training infrastructure to quickly translate field training and education requirements into easily accessible, usable, and effective training materials.  Implement an efficient, open, and consistent process for defining and establishing priorities for IT training requirements.  Create a process to facilitate rapid response to new or changing training priorities within any fiscal year. Identify the requirements, which cannot be met due to resource limitations or additions to training priorities, and raise them to senior management.  Establish an effective evaluation process to ensure trainees is reaping the intended benefits of training. Involve local supervisors in assessing the impact of training on job performance and providing feedback to the Team.','1','career3','1','1',2,'To be the number one IT company in Bangladesh within four years.  INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(13,'Our Goals','Our Goals','IT Bangla Limited has nearly ten years experience developing, implementing customized solutions for organizations around the country, in more than 20 industries, in public and private sectors, from startups to multinational companies.  IT Bangla Limited customers include health care, engineering / construction firms & owner / operators, manufactures, utility & communication companies, military & intelligence agencies, electricity production and distribution, sea port, finance & banking, government agencies, development agencies and many more. Through their work in many countries, IT Bangla Limited customers make the world safer and more prosperous.','1','goals','1','1',