INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(40,'Windows Server 2008 (Microsoft Certified IT Professional) Training Program','MCITP Overview','The Microsoft Certified IT Professional (MCITP) certification helps validate that an individual has the comprehensive set of skills necessary to perform a particular job role, such as database administrator or enterprise messaging administrator. MCITP certifications build on the technical proficiency measured in the Microsoft Certified Technology Specialist (MCTS) certifications. Therefore, you will earn one or more MCTS certifications on your way to earning an MCITP certification.','1','mcse1','1','1',14,'The Microsoft Certified IT Professional (MCITP) certification helps validate that an individual has the comprehensive set of skills necessary to perform a particular job role, such as database administrator or enterprise messaging administrator. INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(41,'Windows Server 2008 (Microsoft Certified IT Professional) Training Program','MCITP candidate profile','MCITP candidates are IT professionals capable of deploying, building, designing, optimizing, and operating technologies for a particular job role. They make the design and technology decisions necessary to ensure successful technology implementation projects.','1','mcse2','1','1',14,'MCITP candidates are IT professionals capable of deploying, building, designing, optimizing, and operating technologies for a particular job role. They make the design and technology decisions necessary to ensure successful technology implementation projects.','mcse');
