ment Software is the sum of all financial records of salaries for an employee, wages, bonuses and deductions. In accounting, payroll refers to the amount paid to employees for services they provided during a certain period of time. Payroll plays a major role in a company for several reasons.  INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(56,'Attendance Management Software','Attendance Management Software','Tracking and managing time and people attendance at work is a tedious task, especially when it''s a manual system. With this Attendance Management software, it''s simple to get real time information by integrating people and processes through technology.  This software enables error free tracking of employees'' time at work. It collates information from various sources like Punch Card system, leave records, holiday calendars etc. to provide an integrated view of employee attendance. Extensive MIS reports are available at both summary and detailed level.  Features:  Automaticly generate employees daily attendance.  Shift rostering and Shift Scheduling.  Automated Leave Tracking.  Employee''s daily and monthly Attendance Report.  Deprtment wish summary report.  Manual Attendance.  Employee''s Previous Attendance Report.  More than 30 type of Attendance Report.  No exatra cost to track employee''s attendance.','1','ams1','11','1',27,'Tracking and managing time and people attendance at work is a tedious task, especially when it''s a manual system. INSERT INTO "smpool_app_website_content_info" VALUES(57,'Overview:','Overview:','This 2-day course designed to expose participants to all the key components of a Mission Critical Data Centre, its operations and maintenance. The course will also provide tips on how to improve current Data Centre effectiveness and maintenance routines affecting Data Center performance in order to improve high availability.','1','cdcp1','1','1',31,'This 2-day course designed to expose participants to all the key components of a Mission